An EmacsLisp blog engine built on [[Elnode]].

Skinny is in development. You can see the source in it's [[http://github.com/nicferrier/Skinny|Github]].

== The point ==

The point of Skinny is to have a simple blogging system in the style of a //Bliki//.

Skinny uses Creole marked-up files for entries.

Skinny can be configured using customize variables.

It's easy to get running by using `elnode-start'.
